v0.1.0.description: First available version of Archipelago.BatBoy. Shuffles seeds and abilities from levels, as well as the red seeds and a single hp up from the shop. Any subsequent HP ups purchased from the shop will function as normal. No randomization options currently but should function as advertised.
v0.1.0.title: Pre-Release 0.1.0

v0.1.5.description:
## What's Changed
* Readme: Flow + formatting + punctuation edits by @SoldierofOrder
* Fix bugs and add some nice new things by @alwaysintreble
* Death link by @alwaysintreble
* items and locations are now sent immediately upon collection, and the cassettes in helsia's shop and the groovy house are now checks. Cassettes still don't exist as items at this time as there's no way to do it.

## New Contributors
* @SoldierofOrder made their first contribution in https://github.com/alwaysintreble/Archipelago.BatBoy/pull/11

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/alwaysintreble/Archipelago.BatBoy/compare/v0.1.0...v0.1.5
